Package: puppetdb-terminus
Architecture: all
Depends: puppet-common, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Puppet data warehouse -- Puppet master terminus
 PuppetDB collects data generated by Puppet. It enables advanced Puppet
 features like exported resources, and can be the foundation for other
 applications that use Puppetâ€™s data.
 .
 This package contains an add-on that allows a Puppet master to use PuppetDB
 for storing and retrieving facts, catalogs and resources.
